Name: ManagedRepresentationReference
Description: Substitution group head for referencing Managed Representations. For example, ManagedTextRepresentationReference, ManagedNumericRepresentationReference, etc.

Name: CategorySchemeReference
Description: A reference to a CategoryScheme as the managed component of a representation.

Name: CodeListReference
Description: A reference to a CodeList as the managed component of a representation.

Name: GeographicStructureReference
Description: A reference to a GeographicStructure as the managed component of a representation.

Name: GeographicLocationReference
Description: A reference to a GeographicLocation as the managed component of a representation.

Name: ConceptReference
Description: Reference to a Concept which provides a context for the representation, e.g. Age for a numeric representation.
